              "fill": "#333333",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "Scene 2: デジタル文具セット",
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 16,
              "fontWeight": "bold"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "apr01s2p",
              "name": "s2prompt",
              "fill": "#555555",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "Prompt: A flat lay of digital stationery items — a smart pen, a digital notebook, a stylus, and a compact scanner — arranged neatly on a light wood desk with a small potted plant. Top-down view with even, warm lighting. Clean, minimalist composition with subtle spring colors. High resolution, editorial style.",
              "lineHeight": 1.6,
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 13,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "apr01s2j",
              "name": "s2ja",
              "fill": "#555555",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "Japanese: スマートペン、デジタルノート、スタイラス、コンパクトスキャナーなどのデジタル文具が明るい木目のデスクにきれいに並べられたフラットレイ。小さな鉢植えも添えて。俯瞰アングルで均一な暖かい照明。ミニマルな構図に春らしい淡い色彩。",
              "lineHeight": 1.6,
              "fontFamily": "Inter",
              "fontSize": 13,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
