              "name": "s3prompt",
              "fill": "#555555",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "Prompt: A realistic lifestyle image of a young professional's clean desk with a smart pen resting on a fresh notebook, next to a laptop and a takeout coffee cup. Morning light streaming through large office windows. Background shows an open-plan office with colleagues blurred in the distance. Fresh, optimistic spring morning feel.",
