              "fill": "#555555",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "Prompt: A photorealistic close-up of a hand holding a sleek scan pen gliding over printed text in an open textbook on a wooden desk. A tablet next to it displays the scanned text in real-time OCR. Warm desk lamp lighting from the right. Background shows study materials and a coffee cup softly blurred. Sharp focus on the pen tip touching the page.",
