              "content": "Prompt: A realistic lifestyle shot of a metallic pen-shaped voice recorder placed upright in a pen holder on a clean white meeting room table, next to a spiral notebook with handwritten meeting notes and a glass of water. Bright fluorescent office lighting from above. Background shows a whiteboard with diagrams, softly out of focus. Professional and functional mood.",
