              "content": "Prompt: A top-down lifestyle image of a scan pen and a pen-shaped recorder lying side by side on an open notebook, surrounded by a smartphone, wireless earbuds, and a laptop on a natural wood desk. Soft overhead daylight from a skylight. Clean, organized workspace aesthetic. The devices are the focal point with everything else slightly blurred.",
